<idea-plugin>
    <id>gen-plugin</id>
    <name> auto code generator</name>

    <vendor email="tanoak@qq.com" url="http://www.github.com/tanoak10">tanoak</vendor>

    <version>1.0.0</version>

    <description><![CDATA[

    这是自动生成Dao 、Service层的代码插件
    Mac 下是 cmd+ N ,win下应该是ctrl+enter
    <>
    <img src="https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/9819800-9e245c7fa5d948ee.jpg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240" alt="说明" title="说明"/>
    就可以生成了，注意，生成的实体需要有id字段
        so easy.<br> Enter short description for your plugin here and easy.<br>
    ]]></description>

    <!-- please see http://www.jetbrains.org/intellij/sdk/docs/basics/getting_started/plugin_compatibility.html
         on how to target different products -->
    <!-- uncomment to enable plugin in all products
    <depends>com.intellij.modules.lang</depends>
    -->

    <extensions defaultExtensionNs="com.intellij">
        <!-- Add your extensions here -->
    </extensions>

    <actions>
        <!-- Add your actions here -->
        <action id="GenAction" class="com.tanoak.action.GeneratorAction" text="AutoCode" description="geng auto">
            <add-to-group group-id="GenerateGroup" anchor="last"/>
        </action>
    </actions>
    <depends>com.intellij.modules.java</depends>
</idea-plugin>